{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/Wishlist_us.gif?t=1738263697\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One night, your normal life is shattered when a friend leads you into the fog-covered woods, revealing a long-buried darkness. Drawn into a world of occult practices, ancient creatures, and supernatural forces, you must navigate a terrifying dungeon and uncover the truth behind the dark ritual.\u00a0The deeper you go, the more you realize you're not just a bystander - you\u2019re the main prey on tonight\u2019s menu.\u00a0Make choices that determine your fate\u00a0and uncover the truth behind the ancient rite before it\u2019s too late.\u00a0Will you escape the blood-stained curse, or become its next victim?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Experience a dynamic and visually rich narrative.</strong> Each moment and shift in the story is uniquely illustrated, immersing you in a world that responds to every action and change in emotion. Complementing this is a diverse musical score, reflecting every twist in the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/Untitled__616_x_246_px___1_.gif?t=1738263697\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Make friends, confront enemies, and question the true intentions of those around you.</strong> Can you decipher their true motives and make the right choices to ensure your survival?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/Characters.png?t=1738263697\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join our community on Discord</strong> to stay updated on the game's development and get access to exclusive content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/Discord_Pic_1.png?t=1738263697\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Listen to some of the masterfully composed music for the novel.</strong> An orchestral score brings the game world to life with upbeat, optimistic tunes and ominous, foreboding compositions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/Soundcloud_pic.png?t=1738263697\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Keep checking back for updates and be ready to immerse yourself in &quot;Sanguis: Veil of the Forgotten&quot;. </strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738263697","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738263697","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738263697","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738263697","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The video game features graphic depictions of violence, including blood and scenes of torture. If you are not prepared for this product, we kindly ask that you refrain from purchasing it."},"demos":[{"appid":2544420,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/Wishlist_us.gif?t=1738263697\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One night, your normal life is shattered when a friend leads you into